nodes.text: Star Wars: R2-D2 and X-Wing Book and Model Sets

Star Wars: R2-D2 and X-Wing Book and Model Sets is a model kit in the Star Wars IncrediBuilds series and a compendium of the previously published titles Star Wars: R2-D2 Deluxe Book and Model Set and Star Wars: X-Wing Deluxe Book and Model Set. It was written by Michael Kogge and published by Insight Editions in 2017.
